content: I think I'll start with the Night Huntress series for now, but I'll keep those recommendations in mind for future reads. I've been enjoying the fantasy romance genre a lot lately, and I'm excited to dive into a new series. By the way, have you heard of Taylor Jenkins Reid? I just discovered her "Maybe in Another Life" series and devoured it in 4 days. I loved her writing style so much that I even pre-ordered her new book, which comes out in August.
